            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Priests"><name
                                ref="Sundipertus/Sprincho de Vico Agello"
                            >Sundiperto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>, qui et Sprincho vocor, filio
                                <persName><name ref="Fardulus">Ferduli</name></persName>, havitator
                        in <rs key="#Vici">vico</rs> prope <rs key="#Baptismal_churches">plebe</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/607"
                            >Sancti Martini</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Dioecesis">diocese</rs> Lucense <foreign>con il consenso del padre
                            ha chiesto a</foreign> domno et viro beatissimo <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/343">Peredeo</persName> in Dei nomine <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >epsicopo</rs>, ut cum tua licentia et iussione trasmutare devirem <rs
                            key="#Churches">eclesia</rs> beati <orgName
                            key="#Casalini/fundamenta #Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/608">Sancti
                            Quirici</orgName> in meliore edificio et <rs key="#Casalini/fundamenta"
                            >fundamento</rs> restaurando et meliorando, <foreign>vendendo
                            accontentato. Ora promette al vescovo per sé e per i successori di non
                            sottrarre la chiesa </foreign>de sub tua potestate et de successoribus
                        tuis (…), et omni tempore in festivitate sancti Quirici recipere et
                        gubernare debeamus <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> illo qui in eclesia et
                        plebe Sancti Martini rector et gubernator fuerit; et ut in ipsa festivitate
                        ividem ipse presbiter officium et missa precare debeat et eum ad gustare, se
                        sexto, qui ei solacii fuerint ipso officio faciendo, bene gubernare debeamus
                        et pleniter sine aliqua dispectione, et offerta ei medietate in ipsa
                        festivitate sancti Quirici dare debeamus. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: auri
                        soledos nomero centum (…). Et quod menime superius memoravimus, iam per
                        annos quadraginta et amplius ipsa eclesia Sancti Quirici sub potestate de
                        ipsa plebe vestra Sancti Martini pertenuit, et modo in suprascripto ordine
                        decernimus, ut cunctis diebus debeat pertinere. (…) Actum in <placeName
                            ref="#places/186" key="#Vici #Churches">Agello</placeName>, ad <rs
                            key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/609">Sancte
                        Marie</orgName>. <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: (ss) Sundipertus
                        presbiter; + Ferduli genitori eius consentientis; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Priests"><name ref="Deusdona">Deusdona</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Celsus">Celso</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>; + <persName key="#Witness #Priests"
                                ><name ref="Audibertus de Agello">Audipert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiteri</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/186"
                            >Agello</placeName> testis; + <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Bruningus">Bruninghi</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Brunari">Brunari</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Quercito</placeName>; + <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Rotchis"
                            >Rotchis</name></persName>
                                <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerici</rs> filio <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Soldulus"
                                >Solduli</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiteri</rs> testis. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>:
                            <persName key="#Writer #Deacons"><name ref="Osprandus"
                            >Osprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                        <p>MDL IV/1, p. 359 nt. 233; MDL V/2, n. 89; CDL II, 181, pp. 155-157; ChLA,
                    XXXIII, 983.</p>
                    </div>
