                    <div type="commentary">
                         <p><foreign>Nota dorsale (sec. XI-XII)</foreign>: In plebe de Agello est
                    una capella Sancti Quirici de eadem plebe. <foreign>Nota dorsale (sec. VIII,
                        Osprandus)</foreign>: Promissio Sprinculi presbiteri de Collis.
                        <foreign>Nota dorsale (sec. XII)</foreign>: De Sancto Quirico. <foreign>Nota
                        dorsale (sec. XI-XII)</foreign>: Repromissio a Sprinco presbitero de
                    ecclesia Sancti Quirici in plebe Agello.</p>
